*&quot;Strange Blues&quot; (Prestige, 1957)
*&quot;Fat Jazz&quot; (Jubilee, 1958)
With The Prestige All Stars
*&quot;Interplay for 2 Trumpets and 2 Tenors&quot; (Prestige, 1957)

